Build:
go build -o terraform-provider-cloudcasa
go build -o terraform-provider-cloudcasa.exe  (windows)

provider must be copied to plugins location
Windows based system %APPDATA%\terraform.d\plugins\${host_name}/${namespace}/${type}/${version}/${target}

%APPDATA%\terraform.d\plugins\cloudcasa.io/cloudcasa/cloudcasa/0.0.1/windows_amd64 (windows)

LINUX
~/.terraform.d/plugins/cloudcasa.io/cloudcasa/cloudcasa/0.0.1/linux_amd64

sudo mv terraform-provider-cloudcasa ~/.terraform.d/plugins/cloudcasa.io/cloudcasa/cloudcasa/0.0.1/linux_amd64/

terraform init -upgrade

https://learn.hashicorp.com/tutorials/terraform/provider-setup?in=terraform/providers

